    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pair A Dice - Fuzzy Dice Edition</strong> includes <strong>Fuzzy Dice</strong> (duh), <strong> 20 Sided Dice</strong>, a <strong>Gamemode</strong>, <strong>1 Emote, </strong>and <strong>4 Unique Cosmetics </strong>to show off your favorite robotic fashion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/13c5f2f6ed92beb7b5a3568aedd0195c.poster.avif?t=1753982369\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/13c5f2f6ed92beb7b5a3568aedd0195c.webm?t=1753982369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/13c5f2f6ed92beb7b5a3568aedd0195c.mp4?t=1753982369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cosmetics:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fuzzy Dice</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gold Aura</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rainbow Robot</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hula Skirt and Coconut Bra</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Color Picker</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beach Ball Emote</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gold Name in Lobby Browser</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Extra Settings:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dice Size</strong>: Roll in style using unpredictable <i><strong>20 Sided Dice!</strong></i> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spawn Menu</strong>: Spawn anything you want except for a loving wife and kids!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Object Collision</strong>: Ride crabs like skateboards and take to the skies on wood planks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Respawns</strong>: Show those really annoying bosses whos boss!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Set Seed</strong>: Enjoy the <i>dice rolling game</i> with &quot;less&quot; randomization!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lobby Name</strong>: Are you speedrunning? Experimenting? Let the world know!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GameJam Gamemode:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense chase Simulator inspired by Dead By Daylight! - Made in 48 hours :)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/4f12fc6d67315c602c6090567f4cf089.poster.avif?t=1753982369\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/4f12fc6d67315c602c6090567f4cf089.webm?t=1753982369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324190/extras/4f12fc6d67315c602c6090567f4cf089.mp4?t=1753982369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
